msgstr "परदा रिमोट"

#: includes/class-wp-curtain-raiser-remote.php:101
msgid "You do not have permission to access this page."
msgstr "आपको इस पेज तक पहुंचने की अनुमति नहीं है।"

#: includes/class-wp-curtain-raiser-remote.php:127
#: includes/class-wp-curtain-raiser-remote.php:212
